@onechampionship first ever 🇺🇸 show, first fight of the night and first TKO of the night. No better feeling than executing your strategy and game plan to a T 🩸. Thank you to my opponent, @diandramartin for stepping in that cage with me! Thank you to my coach @bryanpopejoy for the countless hours he puts into making me the best version I can possibly be, this is nowhere near achievable without you! And to my strength coach @speedofsport for always pushing my limits and leveling me up in every possible way. I have a team of aces around me and I wouldn’t have it any other way. Thank you to my sponsors for being Team Jackie B 🩵 @infightstyle @elitegardencbd and @tikysirisutepopejoy for being the best corner/cheerleader! Thank you @yodchatri for putting me on such a historic event :)

I am beyond excited to announce that the launch of the next full length instructional volume to hit the Warrior Marketplace is with none other than globally renowned striking coach and head honcho at the phenomenal @boxingworks gym in Los Angeles @bryanpopejoy 🤯😍🔥🥋

“Muay Thai Fight IQ - The Counter Fighting System” sees Bryan dig even deeper into his coaching brilliance as he leads this masterclass on to both develop and fight elite level counter fighters!!

Over three hours of truly outstanding Muay Thai, you are not going to want to miss this!! Click on the link below the video to learn more!!

Here, in this clip I took of Bryan whilst I was over in LA filming with him for this volume, he (alongside the equally amazing @jackiebuntan) goes over some drills he likes to use with his fighters when helping them learn to create angles away from forward moving opponents 🔥🔥

Soak in the striking mastery on display, grab yourself some copies of Bryan’s exceptional volumes and the make sure you smash the follow button on him, Jackie and Boxing Works across all social media today 🤯🥋😍🔥
